graph LR
    Kueue[Kueue Controller]

    %% External Dependencies
    Kueue -->|core platform| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.25+]
    Kueue -.->|optional certs| CertManager[cert-manager]
    Kueue -.->|optional metrics| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Kueue -->|queue ML training jobs| TrainingOp[Kubeflow Training Operator]
    Kueue -->|queue Ray workloads| RayOp[Ray Operator]
    Kueue -->|queue multi-job workflows| JobSetOp[JobSet Controller]

    %% Integration Points
    K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server] -->|API server| Kueue
    Kueue -->|watch/reconcile| K8sAPI
    Kueue -->|autoscaling requests| ClusterAutoscaler[cluster-autoscaler]
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrape metrics| Kueue

    %% Job Types Managed
    subgraph "Job Types Managed"
        BatchJob[Batch Jobs]
        PyTorchJob[PyTorchJob]
        TFJob[TFJob]
        MPIJob[MPIJob]
        XGBoostJob[XGBoostJob]
        MXJob[MXJob]
        PaddleJob[PaddleJob]
        RayJob[RayJob]
        RayCluster[RayCluster]
        JobSet[JobSet]
        Pod[Pod]
    end

    TrainingOp -->|provides| PyTorchJob
    TrainingOp -->|provides| TFJob
    TrainingOp -->|provides| MPIJob
    TrainingOp -->|provides| XGBoostJob
    TrainingOp -->|provides| MXJob
    TrainingOp -->|provides| PaddleJob
    RayOp -->|provides| RayJob
    RayOp -->|provides| RayCluster
    JobSetOp -->|provides| JobSet
    Kubernetes -->|provides| BatchJob
    Kubernetes -->|provides| Pod

    Kueue -.->|queues| BatchJob
    Kueue -.->|queues| PyTorchJob
    Kueue -.->|queues| TFJob
    Kueue -.->|queues| MPIJob
    Kueue -.->|queues| XGBoostJob
